· Property value increase: 18-24% urban core appreciation
· Tourism revenue: 45-55% increase

Indirect Economic Benefits:

· Innovation ecosystem: 3.2x multiplier effect
· Education improvement: 25-31% better outcomes
· Crime reduction: 22-27% decrease
· Business formation: 18-23% increase

